            <p>Sorry, but this won't be accepted at this time.</p>

<p>The reason numeric values are not allowed as names of elements, sub forms, and display groups has to do with a design decision to allow overloading to retrieve each of these items. Overloading requires valid PHP variable names.</p>

<p>There are a number of requests similar to yours, and we will likely re-evaluate this decision for 2.0; however before then, making such a change would break existing behavior.</p>

